<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink132-kilavi">
        vāyilvēṇṭivanta pāṇaṉ nīr koṭumai kūṟa vēṇṭa, nummēl aruḷuṭaiyar eṉṟāṟkut talaimakaḷ colliyatu.</p>    <p xml:lang="en">
          Spoken by the heroine to him who said ‘There is no need to speak of your sorrows; he is one with grace upon you’ - [him being] the bard that came, desiring entry.
 </p>
 </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink132">
<l>amma vāḻi pāṇa puṉṉai</l>
<l>yarumpumali kāṉa livvū</l>
<l>ralarā kiṉṟava raruḷu māṟē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
  <l>Oh bard, listen! The way he has graced [me]</l>
    <l>Has become gossip in this town with a seashore grove</l>
    <l>In which buds of the Puṉṉai tree are abundant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
